      <method name="get_oars_value"
              c:identifier="mct_app_filter_get_oars_value"
              version="0.2.0">
        <doc xml:space="preserve"
             filename="libmalcontent/app-filter.c"
             line="602">Get the value assigned to the given @oars_section in the OARS filter stored
within @filter.

If that section has no value explicitly defined,
[enum@Malcontent.AppFilterOarsValue.UNKNOWN] is returned.

This value is the most intense value allowed for apps to have in this
section, inclusive. Any app with a more intense value for this section must
be hidden from the user whose @filter this is.

This does not factor in
[method@Malcontent.AppFilter.is_system_installation_allowed].</doc>
