      <method name="get_daily_limit"
              c:identifier="mct_session_limits_get_daily_limit"
              version="0.14.0">
        <doc xml:space="preserve"
             filename="libmalcontent/session-limits.c"
             line="167">Get the daily limit, if set.

If set, sessions are allowed to be up to the given limit in length every day.

