              version="0.14.0">
        <doc xml:space="preserve"
             filename="libmalcontent/session-limits.c"
             line="786">Set the session limits in @builder to be a daily limit, where the total
active session time for the user has a given limit each day.

@daily_limit_secs must be at most `24 * 60 * 60`.

This will act in addition to any other session limits.</doc>
