    <function name="web_filter_validate_domain_name"
              c:identifier="mct_web_filter_validate_domain_name"
              moved-to="WebFilter.validate_domain_name"
              version="0.14.0">
      <doc xml:space="preserve"
           filename="libmalcontent/web-filter.c"
           line="426">Validate a potential domain name.

This checks against [RFC 2181](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc2181).

See [func@Malcontent.WebFilter.validate_hostname] for validating
hostnames instead. Domain names are entries in the DNS database, hostnames
are website addresses. Every hostname is a domain name, but not vice-versa.</doc>
      <source-position filename="libmalcontent/web-filter.h" line="146"/>
      <return-value transfer-ownership="none">
        <doc xml:space="preserve"
             filename="libmalcontent/web-filter.c"
